org.sbml.jsbml.ext.multi

Class SpeciesFeature

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.AbstractTreeNode
      • org.sbml.jsbml.AbstractSBase
        • org.sbml.jsbml.AbstractNamedSBase
          • org.sbml.jsbml.ext.multi.SpeciesFeature
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode, ListOfSpeciesFeatureContent, NamedSBase, SBase, TreeNodeWithChangeSupport

    public class SpeciesFeature
extends AbstractNamedSBase
implements ListOfSpeciesFeatureContent
    Defines the state of a component in a species by selecting values from the listOfPossibleSpeciesFeatureValues of the referenced SpeciesFeatureType.
    Since:
    1.1
    Author:
    Nicolas Rodriguez
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
